HEADWORD: Arundelian
<hw>Ar`un*del"ian</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to
an Earl of Arundel; <as>as, Arundel or <ex>Arundelian</ex> marbles,
marbles from ancient Greece, bought by the Earl of Arundel in
1624</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
